{"tid":1713173,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"土瓜灣絕對需要set rb 11-13","createTime":"2019-11-12T16:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T14:53:06.000Z","uid":338634,"like":145,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":122,"replies":[{"pid":"e4db94fd14dcc2669cba2e7676eeafcc70785425","tid":1713173,"uid":338634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩聽日 手足幫幫忙係<strong>土瓜灣set rb</strong><br />\n因為基本上過海既巴士都一定要經土瓜灣條大路轉返上去過海隧道<br />\n所以<br />\n土瓜灣一塞 <br />\n就所有去尖沙咀同過海既車都玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n觀塘、旺角、將軍澳d巴士線都拜拜得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢兩日<br />\n吾知點解紅隧都順暢到不得了<br />\n仲塞少過平時返工時間<br />\n我地要命中要害<br />\n用最少最省資源 發揮最大功效<br />\n<br />\n最後 <br />\n各位手足 早d休息"},{"pid":"e55a099dd7b82f111a39292b2d3efe5d9a242f85","tid":1713173,"uid":229156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:32:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"762c20a6e25ce2efdb4cc8d067202dfb40b70fbf","tid":1713173,"uid":221079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:32:56.000Z","msg":"三罷！！！<br />\n全港RB！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b76120942039b80988fa4205ce3c1c0cdbad373","tid":1713173,"uid":273587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:34:52.000Z","msg":"P push"},{"pid":"7ffa5130c7a621fa36b8d0415946624679a9d1a8","tid":1713173,"uid":54774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:36:08.000Z","msg":"曱近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637c1aac5871835b1f2